{"tid":701687,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[本土broadgame]我同班fd整咗隻北韓broadgame","createTime":"2018-06-14T10:11:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-03T14:07:20.000Z","uid":28181,"like":56,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ed5b72aa606695605d9ef8fe283f759a3f7e0610","tid":701687,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T10:11:42.000Z","msg":"是咁的，趁住特金會個議題炒到㷫烚烚小弟整咗隻卡game嚟贈下興<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同各位巴打絲打一齊企喺金正恩特朗普文在寅嘅角色做決策過下世界領袖癮。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/180234_d6c76ad032ed23a7dc48591dc04e8fa9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F180234_d6c76ad032ed23a7dc48591dc04e8fa9.png&h=3530b8f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n整game嘅途中得到好多朋友落力幫手支持先至可以去到呢步<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不過小弟係第一次整board game所以請各位巴絲打多多指教。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n隻game叫做「Brinkmanship」，中文即係邊緣博弈，意思係指金正恩同特朗普呢排大玩特玩嘅「尋日互hi今日friend番」嘅懸崖戰術。隻game嘅design已經做好咗但係rulebook仲未finalize，隻game嘅內容主要就係日本，中國，俄羅斯，美國，南韓同北韓嘅外交角力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/japan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/russia.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/south_korea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/180308_2be246fd9a4cc144218cab9be5b56064.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F180308_2be246fd9a4cc144218cab9be5b56064.png&h=3439ee6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁點樣角力法呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/battle.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖然每個國家嘅目標都唔同，但係某啲國家例如中國同俄羅斯，美國同日本會有差唔多嘅目標，咁幾時互相合作幾時係背後插佢一刀就係呢個遊戲嘅精髓嘞。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/kill_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/180326_12f9640f871d715a8af02b408e97b17c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F180326_12f9640f871d715a8af02b408e97b17c.png&h=d37f1a4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/14/180338_dd442e3ef431f56183a78e3f1c9d991f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F14%2F180338_dd442e3ef431f56183a78e3f1c9d991f.png&h=fd395469&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家仲構思緊一個後續玩法，就係跟返現實再現返金正恩同意朝鮮半島無核化之後嘅世界角力，不過詳細點玩仲未諗好。有冇巴打有好提議?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我哋facebook page係<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/BrinkmanshipHongKong \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FBrinkmanshipHongKong%20&d=3ixQF1WCGVff7VOvrrywgRFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=e4e7a201\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/BrinkmanshipHongKong </a><br />\n各位巴打得閒就上嚟望吓啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b9233c70337643bfd206e14b8e002799d8bbcd7","tid":701687,"uid":84286,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T10:20:15.000Z","msg":"高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e317ed91bc4390bbb8a041b9b4f384552eac6dbd","tid":701687,"uid":28181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0b9233c70337643bfd206e14b8e002799d8bbcd7","tid":701687,"uid":84286,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T10:20:15.000Z","msg":"高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T10:27:15.000Z","ms